Reasoning: 
1. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - This paper focuses on cellular networks and their analysis, which falls under the domain of networking and internet architecture. 
2. cs.IT (Information Theory) - The paper discusses signal-to-interference-plus-noise-ratio and its related performance metrics, which are related to information theory. 
3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper discusses power control, which is related to systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses transmission rate analysis, which is related to multimedia. 
5. cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems) - Although not a primary focus, the paper discusses interference protection around receivers, which can be related to multi-agent systems.
